    • Method Detail

      • matches

        boolean matches(Request r)
        Returns true if the given request matches the filter. matches(Request, Enrollment) is called with the current assignment.

      • matches

        boolean matches(Request r,
                Enrollment e)
        Returns true if the given request with the given assignment matches the filter.

      • matches

        boolean matches(Student s)
        Returns true if the given student matches the filter. This means that a student has a request that matches the filter.

      • matches

        boolean matches(Course c)
        Returns true if the given course matches the filter. This means that a student has a request for the course that matches the filter.
